                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.00/7176: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">MacMurray</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Peking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1926-03-13T16:00:00+08:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 13, 1926—4 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received March 13—9:12 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>125. My number 123, March 12, 7 p.m. Naval commanders at Tientsin have found it
                    necessary because of practical difficulties to request delay of one day in
                    making the contemplated notification to Chinese military and naval authorities.
                    I have approved.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">MacMurray</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
